<p><a href="https://gitlab.gnome.org/GNOME/gnome-contacts">Contacts</a> can now import multiple vCard files at once and preview the contacts you&rsquo;re about to import to avoid any mistakes. Already part of the 46.alpha release, so grab it while it&rsquo;s hot!

